---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-via-black sm:text-4xl">
        Training Agenda
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">
        A structured approach to mastering strategic conversations and getting executive buy-in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- M1: Building the Business Case -->
      <div class="bg-via-light rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-black relative flex items-center justify-center p-8">
          <img src={`${base}/via-assets/Buildup/Vision.svg`} alt="" class="max-h-full w-auto object-contain opacity-90 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-black font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Building the Business Case</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Stop pitching "culture" and start pitching "results." Learn how to calculate the <strong>Cost of Inaction</strong> to make your proposals undeniable to leadership.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- M2: The Physiology of Conflict -->
      <div class="bg-via-light rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-black relative flex items-center justify-center p-8">
          <img src={`${base}/via-assets/Buildup/Direction.svg`} alt="" class="max-h-full w-auto object-contain opacity-90 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-black font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">2</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">The Physiology of Conflict</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Understand why humans are biologically wired to avoid tough talks and how to manage the <strong>"gut response"</strong> that blocks progress in meetings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- M3: The Cost of Avoidance -->
      <div class="bg-via-light rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-black relative flex items-center justify-center p-8">
          <img src={`${base}/via-assets/Buildup/Alignment.svg`} alt="" class="max-h-full w-auto object-contain opacity-90 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-black font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">3</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">The Cost of Avoidance</h3>
          <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm space-y-2">
            <p><strong>Reset:</strong> Techniques to clear the mind and enter a "flow state".</p>
            <p><strong>The 3F Framework:</strong> Acknowledge tension and speak truth without defensiveness.</p>
            <p><strong>Emptying the Bottle:</strong> Ensure every perspective is heard for 100% buy-in.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
